34
00:02:24,870 --> 00:02:27,290
How do you come up with the most appropriate
plan?

35
00:02:27,290 --> 00:02:29,330
Well, that’s indeed the tricky part.

36
00:02:29,330 --> 00:02:30,569
Every context requires adaptation.

37
00:02:30,569 --> 00:02:34,120
National legislation, when existing, must
lead the way.

38
