The proximity of neighbor communities
And the existing financial and human resources.

49
00:03:35,959 --> 00:03:39,640
The specific steps in the process may vary.

50
00:03:39,640 --> 00:03:46,530
The objective is always the same: safely reduce
the risk of infection spreading.

51
00:03:46,530 --> 00:03:53,320
So finally, how does a system of medical waste
management look like?

52
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:58,459
How do you do if you have to get rid of sharp
objects such as needles, scalpel or broken

53
