55
00:04:06,819 --> 00:04:08,439
We need to start with the segregation.

56
00:04:08,439 --> 00:04:12,959
The simplest option might be to use only a
Safety box.

57
00:04:12,959 --> 00:04:20,000
A paper carton box, widely available everywhere
in the world, specifically designed and labelled

58
