sharp pit.

62
00:04:32,140 --> 00:04:36,730
The operations behind each step need to be
correctly performed.

63
00:04:36,730 --> 00:04:41,980
Hospital staff need to be properly equipped
and trained.

64
00:04:41,980 --> 00:04:48,350
