not because it shows an environment dirty
and not well kept, but because it does not

74
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:34,770
accomplish to principle of reducing the risk
for the users of the health facility.

75
00:05:34,770 --> 00:05:42,170
Those boxes left unattended, are a temptation
for the kids, they can easy spill over and

76
